text: Adolf Hellquist (30 August 1901 - 9 December 1971) was a Swedish diver. He competed in two events at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1901 births Category:1971 deaths Category:Swedish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Sweden Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
